It's so convenient, and no extra charge!
And we LOVE the pan-fried pot stickers and Mongolian Beef.
The rice is nice and sticky, just the way I like it.
The price is right too.
This is definitely our favorite traditional Chinese place.
We haven't ventured beyond the Chinese food menu to try the sushi.

